    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《保护松谷》是一款轻度罗格（Rogue）战术游戏，您将率领军团跨越不同环境进行连续作战。每场战斗中可自由切换两种模式：在指挥官模式下俯瞰战场调兵遣将，或切入士兵模式亲临火线，以第三人称操控任一单位扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189670/extras/48a795e9c004397e6dbe88c8afeccb39.poster.avif?t=1771473257\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189670/extras/48a795e9c004397e6dbe88c8afeccb39.webm?t=1771473257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189670/extras/48a795e9c004397e6dbe88c8afeccb39.mp4?t=1771473257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次征程将在分支式战场地图上展开。凯旋后可选择强化部队、招募新兵，或解锁指挥官/士兵双模式的新技能。需谨慎规划行军路线——不同战场环境将带来迥异的奖励与机遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189670/extras/80d40b25b07cc0dc66dec8831f609e92.poster.avif?t=1771473257\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189670/extras/80d40b25b07cc0dc66dec8831f609e92.webm?t=1771473257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189670/extras/80d40b25b07cc0dc66dec8831f609e92.mp4?t=1771473257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏允许多元化通关方式：全程运筹帷幄，每战身先士卒，或双模式动态切换。随着进程推进，您将打造专属强化路线：或增强士兵模式操控单位，或解锁指挥官专属技能。如何保护松谷皆由您自主抉择。</p>",
